TYPE ERRORS TO FIX:

@tevm/txpool: src/TxPool.ts:85:2 - error TS4114: This member must have an 'override' modifier because it overrides a member in the base class 'TxPool'.
@tevm/evm: src/createEvm.js:78:15 - error TS18048: 'step.opcode.dynamicFee' is possibly 'undefined'.
